{"id":14955,"date":"2021-05-10T13:59:47","date_gmt":"2021-05-10T08:29:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/?page_id=14955"},"modified":"2023-04-24T15:59:11","modified_gmt":"2023-04-24T10:29:11","slug":"goa","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/destination-wedding\/goa\/","title":{"rendered":"Goa Destination Wedding"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50px&#8221; el_class=&#8221;height30&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;flexrow&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243; el_class=&#8221;flextwo gt-custom-sidebar-column&#8221;][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id=&#8221;destination-package-international-sidebar&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;3\/4&#8243; el_class=&#8221;second-div-text flexone&#8221;][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Tips For a Destination Wedding in Goa&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before planning a destination wedding in Goa, there are a couple of things you should remember to ensure you have the destination wedding of your dreams. Visit the venue beforehand so that everything is to your liking and you know how you want the venue to look like for every wedding event. Meet the vendor&#8217;s way prior to your wedding so all the details can be discussed properly and there is no misunderstanding at the last minute. Tailor your wedding dress according to the chosen destination, look up the local marriage requirements, and secure all the necessary travel documents.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Cost of Goa Destination Wedding Package&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Goa destination wedding cost will depend on the package you choose and the features you decide to add to it. The cost will vary depending on whether you wish to add other events to the wedding, the venue you select, and so on.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Best Part of Goa for A Destination Wedding&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ATW Travels offers some of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/package\/goa-tour-package\/\">best destination wedding places in Goa<\/a> for our customers to choose from. Some of the places include Old Goa, Baga, Panaji, Cavelossim, Vagator, and Anjuna.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Best Goa Beach for Destination Wedding&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A beach destination wedding in Goa is always a good idea. Goa has several amazing beaches for you to choose from, such as Colva Beach, Dona Paula Beach, Morjim Beach, Palolem Beach, Vagator Beach, Galgibaga Beach, Benaulim Beach, Calangute Beach, Agonda Beach, Arambol Beach, Candolim Beach, Anjuna Beach, Butterfly Beach, and Cavelossim Beach.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Best Goa Resorts to Stay in For Destination Wedding&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you want to know about the best destination wedding resorts in Goa, ATW Travels has it covered. There are numerous resorts where you can have your weddings, such as Taj Resort &amp; Convention Centre, Agonda Serenity Resort, Andores Resort And Spa, Art Resort, Patnem Garden Resort, Seashell Suites and Villas, Seashell Beach Suites, Doubletree By Hilton, Radisson Blu Resort, Kings Villa Resort, The Leela, and Novotel Goa Resort &amp; Spa. Some other luxurious resorts at Goa for a destination wedding include Acron Waterfront Resort, Heritage Village Resort &amp; Spa, Shanti Morada, Jacks Resort, Hacienda De Goa Resort, and Nanu Resort.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Get to know about our daily offers by visiting our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/atwtravels.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Instagram Profile<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner]<div class=\"st-faq-new st-faq\">\r\n    <h4>FAQs About Our Goa Destination Wedding Packages<\/h4>\r\n                                <div class=\"item active\">\r\n                    <div class=\"header\">\r\n                        <i class=\"input-icon field-icon fa\"><svg height=\"18px\" width=\"18px\" version=\"1.1\" id=\"Layer_1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\"\r\n     viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"enable-background:new 0 0 24 24;\" xml:space=\"preserve\">\r\n\r\n<g fill=\"#5E6D77\">\r\n    <path d=\"M5.25,24c-0.116,0-0.232-0.027-0.336-0.079C4.659,23.793,4.5,23.536,4.5,23.25V19.5H2.25C1.009,19.5,0,18.491,0,17.25v-15\r\n        C0,1.009,1.009,0,2.25,0h19.5C22.991,0,24,1.009,24,2.25v15c0,1.241-1.009,2.25-2.25,2.25H11.5l-5.8,4.35\r\n        C5.571,23.947,5.411,24,5.25,24z M2.25,1.5C1.836,1.5,1.5,1.836,1.5,2.25v15C1.5,17.664,1.836,18,2.25,18h3\r\n        C5.664,18,6,18.336,6,18.75v3l4.8-3.6c0.129-0.097,0.289-0.15,0.45-0.15h10.5c0.414,0,0.75-0.336,0.75-0.75v-15\r\n        c0-0.414-0.336-0.75-0.75-0.75H2.25z\"\/>\r\n    <path d=\"M12,12c-0.414,0-0.75-0.336-0.75-0.75v-0.256c-0.001-0.952,0.602-1.805,1.5-2.122c0.897-0.317,1.5-1.17,1.5-2.121\r\n        c0-0.6-0.234-1.165-0.66-1.59c-0.425-0.426-0.99-0.66-1.59-0.66c-0.601,0-1.166,0.234-1.591,0.659\r\n        C9.984,5.584,9.75,6.149,9.75,6.75C9.75,7.164,9.414